name: JubJub jelly
description:
You are JubJub, the great Jelly dudeguy, man. Run from Hungry Muggins prats, and avoid the super dangerous walls! Run as fast as you can, and try to get the maximum score (Grade)

This game was made for a charity event. I'm currently trying to pay for a surgery and treatment of a tumour, so by paying your actually just donating. I only hope the rage from this game doesn't give others tumors! :)
